snippet.title: SBK™ 22 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The wait is over! #SBK22 will be available on September 15, 2022 for your amazing races with the official riders, tracks and bikes of the current season. Watch the trailer and be ready to get back on track!

📘 Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SBKtheofficialvideogame

📸 Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/sbkvideogame/

📱 Discord: https://discord.gg/GpVnDxF98D

🌍 Website: http://www.sbkvideogame.com/
